name: Flag of No Land
description:
Compression of images, appropriated artworks, scribbles, figures, and text. This is no land, everything is defined as knowledge and education tools for everyone. everything is counted as experience. under one flag of dictating screen that shaped our culture. 

Artworks in frame: Koons, Olafur, Nava, Gormley, Kaprow, Rubens, Beuys, and Christo
